---
title: Carb Smart Loaded Bacon and Pepper Soup with DIY Croutons
description: Carb smart soup can still have you saying, "mmm, good soup!" Bacon and peppers are best friends in this creamy, satisfying soup with red pepper pesto and DIY ciabatta croutons.
